{"tid":2162422,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"總辭的陰謀 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-08-18T06:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T07:32:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a49c5b2c849c73c2728a50615661c043309f90c","tid":2162422,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200723/5G7BPYQM75HETBIIVFNJMHB6LQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200723%2F5G7BPYQM75HETBIIVFNJMHB6LQ%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=01f09876\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200723%2F5G7BPYQM75HETBIIVFNJMHB6LQ%2F&h=bf6eddf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200723/5G7BPYQM75HETBIIVFNJMHB6LQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n總辭的陰謀 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UkA1Ig7p1ZVAzAvlUCJP1LpcSNE=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BIHY3RFLORBHBLFSCZ7YOUKQGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUkA1Ig7p1ZVAzAvlUCJP1LpcSNE%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBIHY3RFLORBHBLFSCZ7YOUKQGA.jpg&h=27813642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是一個無論去或留，泛民都會遍體鱗傷的政治陰謀。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委輕輕放過4個被選舉主任DQ的現役議員，然後讓全體留任至少一年，把「留任」還是「辭任」的難題交給泛民硬食。<br />\n<br />\n而泛民面對甚麼的難處？<br />\n<br />\n第一是「集體行動」，不論留或走，都要集體。問題是，泛民本身光譜不同，如何能讓「本土自決」、「民主抗爭」等等不同派別「集體一致」呢？明明強調「兄弟爬山」，但「集體行動」正正把這種靈活抹走。<br />\n<br />\n泛民初選，單單一張所謂「攬炒聲明」，已經造成嚴重內部分裂。由「內部矛盾」變成「敵我矛盾」。<br />\n<br />\n現在總辭又變成另一次的「道德分裂」，不論留或走，都被當成是「背叛」﹗留低的被抗爭派嘲笑是「嗟來之食」、「戀棧人工」、「無抗爭意志」，而離開的人又被批評是「道德綁架」、「拱手相讓」。<br />\n<br />\n第二是「。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而根據「。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n泛民如果離開，。。。。。。。。。。；泛民如果留下，。。。。。。。。。。，政府仍然很爽。<br />\n<br />\n第三，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n如果我們真的用「認受性」、「正當性」去做行動標準，那麼當參選人被DQ主任無理DQ後，其實所有泛民都不應繼續入閘參選，因為這也是一種「被當權者恩賜入閘」的行為﹗那麼去年黃之鋒被DQ，難道其他抗爭議員都應該退出以凸顯選舉入閘的不公平嗎？<br />\n<br />\n結論是﹕不論留或走，泛民注定大分裂﹗即使搞公投民調，一樣逃不過分化的命運。"},{"pid":"a2e4114fc4604b69ceed4090c63dad69ea5adff0","tid":2162422,"uid":281437,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"有第三條路<br />\n政事台討論中"},{"pid":"0b3a7e05272377950868400eb1961539ef961a05","tid":2162422,"uid":21716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"搞次民間公投囉，好似初選咁搞"},{"pid":"7c285005dc9f61327573425f86a9e14b04de3205","tid":2162422,"uid":197103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"好似初選咁搞都要籌備一排+唔少錢銀<br />\n出來個結果都幾肯定係55波, 對於日後方向係冇咩意思<br />\n<br />\n不如搞民間議會啦"},{"pid":"468c06a234751216a137f6995025a88daf436699","tid":2162422,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"抗爭派辭，泛民留囉"},{"pid":"dd7746683d21ee2559c626ea9388c4184f75ee37","tid":2162422,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"PORI 有民調,  其中一條有問呢樣, 另外有問林鄭值幾多分<br />\n<br />\n請大家入去做民調,   越多人參與民調相對越巨參考價值."},{"pid":"43b02654e903dc5222d0572137c0ca2f13ac514b","tid":2162422,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba976b563cceaa81a1dcc8a15eb61eb19cce2de9","tid":2162422,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43b02654e903dc5222d0572137c0ca2f13ac514b","tid":2162422,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"PORI 有民調, 其中一條有問呢樣, 另外有問林鄭值幾多分<br />\n<br />\n請大家入去做民調, 越多人參與民調相對越巨參考價值."},{"pid":"2515d42d59629c7bf57a69be9f98dde20c71b6eb","tid":2162422,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{